# HS Code Classification Assistant

AI-powered customs product classification system using Mistral LLM, RAG, and Qdrant.

## Features

- HS Code Prediction
- Customs Regulation Retrieval
- RAG Pipeline
- FastAPI API
- QLoRA Fine-Tuning
- Docker Deployment

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Mistral
- FastAPI
- Qdrant
- Docker
- MLflow

